ate kareem ki panah leta hu isse keh jab mera Mahe Ramazan ikhtetaam pazeer (khatm) ho, ya jab meri is raat ki fajr tuloo kare (subh ho) to mere zimme koi gunah ya us par mera giraft (moaakheza) baaqi na ho jis par mujhe azaab de.", "Urdu": "تیری ذات کریم کی پناہ حاصل کرتا ہوں اس سے کہ جب میرا ماہ رمضان اختتام پذیر ہو یا جب میری اس رات کی فجر طلوع کرے تو میرے ذمے کوئی گناہ یا اس پر گرفت باقی ہو جس پر مجھے عذاب دے۔", "RArabic": "A-O’OZO BE-JALAALE WAJHE-KAL KAREE-ME AN YAN-QAZEYA A’NNEE SHAHRO RAMAZAANA AW YATLO-A’L FAJRO MIN LAIY-LATEE HAAZE-HI WA LAKA QEBA-LEE ZAMBUN AW TABE-A’TUN TO-A’ZZE-NONEE A’LAIY-KA.", "ArabicText1": "اَعُوْذُ بِجَلَالِ وَجْہِکَ الْکَرِیْمِ اَنْ یَّنْقَضِیَ عَنِّیْ شَہْرُ رَمَضَانَ اَوْ یَطْلُعَ الْفَجْرُ مِنْ لَیْلَتِیْ ہٰذِہٖ وَلَکَ قِبَلِیْ ذَنْۢبٌ اَوْ تَبِعَۃٌ تُعَذِّبُنِیْ عَلَیْہِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGr